	<summary>A very simple framework for using PHP as a commandline script language.</summary>
	<description>This very simple framework enables a collection of tasks to be defined as methods on a PHP class, and configuration values to be defined in a XML file. The tasks then have easy access to the configuration values as instance variables (declared or dynamic) or via XPath.</description>

